rcpplus
=======

rcpplus is a C implementation of Bosch (formerly known as VCS Video Communication Systems AG) RCP+ version 3 protocol

supported platforms
-------------------
being written in pure c99 it is fairly easy to port this library to any platform including linux, windows, macOS, ...

supported cameras
-----------------
this library has been developed and tested using VG4 AutoDome 300 series, VG4 AutoDome 500 series and Dinion 300 series but it should work with any camera supporting RCP+ version 3.0

requirements
------------
no additional library is required to use this library however you need ffmpeg and SDL inorder to run some of sample codes

contact
-------
if you have any question, suggestion, ... send me an email to arash.cordi[at]gmail.com
